ss="text-right" dir="auto"><!--[-1--><!--[7-->0<!--]--><!--]--></div><!--]--><!--]--></div> <!--[-1--><!--]--></td><td class="group relative min-w-fit max-w-sm break-words p-2 border-l" data-table-row-index="16" data-column-index="12"><div class="line-clamp-2 "><!--[--><!--[-1--><div class="text-right" dir="auto"><!--[-1--><!--[7-->3<!--]--><!--]--></div><!--]--><!--]--></div> <!--[-1--><!--]--></td><td class="group relative min-w-fit max-w-sm break-words p-2 border-l" data-table-row-index="16" data-column-index="13"><div class="line-clamp-2 "><!--[--><!--[-1--><div class="text-right" dir="auto"><!--[-1--><!--[7-->94.228042<!--]--><!--]--></div><!--]--><!--]--></div> <!--[-1--><!--]--></td><!--]--></tr><tr class="group cursor-pointer space-x-4 divide-x border-b outline-offset-[-2px] odd:bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 dark:odd:bg-gray-925 dark:hover:bg-gray-850  last:border-none" tabindex="0" data-row-idx="17" data-table-row-index="17"><!--[--><td class="group relative min-w-fit max-w-sm break-words p-2" data-table-row-index="17" data-column-index="0"><div class="line-clamp-2 "><!--[--><!--[-1--><div dir="auto"><!--[-1--><!--[10--><div><!--[-1--><!--]--> <span class="block ">002ff33a8bc9b69d49e4eb1189914426</span></div> <!--[-1--><!--]--><!--]--><!--]--></div><!--]--><!--]--></div> <!--[-1--><!--]--></td><td class="group relative min-w-fit max-w-sm break-words p-2 border-l" data-table-row-index="17" data-column-index="1"><div class="line-clamp-2 "><!--[--><!--[-1--><div dir="auto"><!--[-1--><!--[10--><div><!--[-1--><!--]--> <span class="block ">o1-preview-2024-09-12</span></div> <!--[-1--><!--]--><!--]--><!--]--></div><!--]--><!--]--></div> <!--[-1--><!--]--></td><td class="group relative min-w-fit max-w-sm break-words p-2 border-l" data-table-row-index="17" data-column-index="2"><div class="line-clamp-2 "><!--[--><!--[-1--><div dir="auto"><!--[-1--><!--[10--><div><!--[-1--><!--]--> <span class="block ">I was trying to make a telegram bot with a web application, in the web application itself there should be a button in the middle and a little bit below the counter of clicks on the button.  Fix and improve the program to make the bot correspond to the condition. 

Code:
```Python 
import telebot
